refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.parameters;




   datetime



     DateTimeImmutable::__construct 接受的日期/时间格式。

&reftitle.changelog;





    &Version;
    &Description;





    7.2.0

     返回数组的 zone 
     键现在代表秒，而不是分钟。并且正负符号已反转，例如：之前是
     -120 现在是 7200。

  &reftitle.examples;



    具有全面的 datetime 字符串的 date_parse 示例


<?php
var_dump(date_parse("2006-12-12 10:00:00.5"));
?>


    &example.outputs;


array(12) {
  'year' => int(2006)
  'month' => int(12)
  'day' => int(12)
  'hour' => int(10)
  'minute' => int(0)
  'second' => int(0)
  'fraction' => double(0.5)
  'warning_count' => int(0)
  'warnings' => array(0) {
  }
  'error_count' => int(0)
  'errors' => array(0) {
  }
  'is_localtime' => bool(false)
}







   如果在指定 datetime
   字符串中出现时区元素，那才会展示。在这种情况下，总会存在
   zone_type 和更多元素，具体取决于其值。

    带时区缩写信息的 date_parse


<?php
var_dump(date_parse("June 2nd, 2022, 10:28:17 BST"));
?>


    &example.outputs;


array(16) {
  'year' => int(2022)
  'month' => int(6)
  'day' => int(2)
  'hour' => int(10)
  'minute' => int(28)
  'second' => int(17)
  'fraction' => double(0)
  'warning_count' => int(0)
  'warnings' => array(0) {
  }
  'error_count' => int(0)
  'errors' => array(0) {
  }
  'is_localtime' => bool(true)
  'zone_type' => int(2)
  'zone' => int(0)
  'is_dst' => bool(true)
  'tz_abbr' => string(3) "BST"
}



    带时区标识符信息的 date_parse


<?php
var_dump(date_parse("June 2nd, 2022, 10:28:17 Europe/London"));
?>


    &example.outputs;


array(14) {
  'year' => int(2022)
  'month' => int(6)
  'day' => int(2)
  'hour' => int(10)
  'minute' => int(28)
  'second' => int(17)
  'fraction' => double(0)
  'warning_count' => int(0)
  'warnings' => array(0) {
  }
  'error_count' => int(0)
  'errors' => array(0) {
  }
  'is_localtime' => bool(true)
  'zone_type' => int(3)
  'tz_id' => string(13) "Europe/London"
}






   如果解析的 datetime 字符串越小，那么可用的信息就越少。再本示例中，所有时间部分都返回为 &false;。

    带最小字符串的 date_parse


<?php
var_dump(date_parse("June 2nd, 2022"));
?>


    &example.outputs;


array(12) {
  'year' => int(2022)
  'month' => int(6)
  'day' => int(2)
  'hour' => bool(false)
  'minute' => bool(false)
  'second' => bool(false)
  'fraction' => bool(false)
  'warning_count' => int(0)
  'warnings' => array(0) {
  }
  'error_count' => int(0)
  'errors' => array(0) {
  }
  'is_localtime' => bool(false)
}






   相对格式不会影响从绝对格式格式化的值，但会被解析为“relative”元素。

    带相对格式的 date_parse


<?php
var_dump(date_parse("2006-12-12 10:00:00.5 +1 week +1 hour"));
?>


    &example.outputs;


array(13) {
  'year' => int(2006)
  'month' => int(12)
  'day' => int(12)
  'hour' => int(10)
  'minute' => int(0)
  'second' => int(0)
  'fraction' => double(0.5)
  'warning_count' => int(0)
  'warnings' => array(0) {
  }
  'error_count' => int(0)
  'errors' => array(0) {
  }
  'is_localtime' => bool(false)
  'relative' =>
  array(6) {
    'year' => int(0)
    'month' => int(0)
    'day' => int(7)
    'hour' => int(1)
    'minute' => int(0)
    'second' => int(0)
  }
}






   在某些时候，比如 Thursday 将会设置字符串的时间部分设置为
   0。如果 Thursday 传递给
   DateTimeImmutable::__construct 也会导致小时，分钟，秒和小数部分设置为
   0。下面的示例中，year 元素将设置为 &false;。

    date_parse with side-effects


<?php
var_dump(date_parse("Thursday, June 2nd"));
?>


    &example.outputs;


array(13) {
  'year' => bool(false)
  'month' => int(6)
  'day' => int(2)
  'hour' => int(0)
  'minute' => int(0)
  'second' => int(0)
  'fraction' => double(0)
  'warning_count' => int(0)
  'warnings' => array(0) {
  }
  'error_count' => int(0)
  'errors' => array(0) {
  }
  'is_localtime' => bool(false)
  'relative' =>
  array(7) {
    'year' => int(0)
    'month' => int(0)
    'day' => int(0)
    'hour' => int(0)
    'minute' => int(0)
    'second' => int(0)
    'weekday' => int(4)
  }
}
